FC Barcelona will play both Real Madrid and Inter 𝐓𝐖𝐈𝐂𝐄 within 15 DAYS! 🤯

These games will be absolutely crucial in deciding FC Barcelona’s season! 

Barça’s Upcoming Fixtures:
• Real Madrid (Copa del Rey final 🏆 )
• Inter (H)
• Real Valladolid (A)
• Inter (A)
• Real Madrid (H)

Barça are one of the few teams still capable of winning the TREBLE this season. If they win all of these matches, they’ll be closer than ever to securing their historic THIRD TREBLE!
